text: Anahita is an Iranian goddess. Anahita may also refer to: *Anahit, an Armenian goddess *Anahita (spider), a genus of spider *Temple of Anahita, Kangavar, archeological site in Kermanshah, Iran *Temple of Anahita, Bishapur, archeological site in Fars, Iran *Temple of Anahita, Khenaman, archeological site in Rafsanjan, Iran *Anahita, a minor planet designation: 270 Anahita ==See also== *Anaïs (disambiguation) *Nahid (disambiguation)
